1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:02:51,989
****翻译:法兰克彼得生****

2
00:03:44,624 --> 00:03:48,182
Why not call it the Pecu?
Or the Nipia one?
为什么不叫它其它什么名？

3
00:03:48,308 --> 00:03:51,101
I'm just saying how do we know
it's an ice age?
我是说为什么我们知道现在是冰河世纪。

4
00:03:51,454 --> 00:03:53,911
Because of all the ices!
就因为这些冰川！

5
00:03:56,097 --> 00:03:58,389
Well , things just
got a little peculiar.
好的，事情变的有点奇怪了。

6
00:03:58,515 --> 00:04:01,886
Help! Help!
救命！救命！

7
00:04:02,045 --> 00:04:05,263
Come on, kids, let's go.
The berg is moving.
别玩了，孩子们。我们走。
灾难就要来了。

8
00:04:05,497 --> 00:04:06,764
But, dad. . .
但是，爸爸....

9
00:04:07,494 --> 00:04:10,134
No "but".
You can play later.
没什么“但是”。
你以后可以玩。

10
00:04:10,526 --> 00:04:12,860
Okay.
Come on, guys.
好的，来吧，兄弟们。

11
00:04:14,170 --> 00:04:16,003
Sally, where's Eddie?
赛利，艾迪在哪？

12
00:04:16,127 --> 00:04:19,806
He said something about being on a
verge of a revolutionary breakthrough.
他说什么：现在是进化突破的关键阶段。

13
00:04:19,927 --> 00:04:21,148
Really?
真的吗？

14
00:04:22,534 --> 00:04:24,871
I'm flying!
我飞了！

15
00:04:26,103 --> 00:04:27,523
Some breakthrough.
这就是一些突破。

16
00:04:29,135 --> 00:04:30,859
Look out!
A mammoth is on its way.
小心呀。
猛玛象来了。

17
00:04:40,111 --> 00:04:42,477
Hey, do the world a favour!
嗨，帮个忙！

18
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,322
Move your issue off the road!
不要挡路。

19
00:04:45,866 --> 00:04:49,663
If my trunk was that small ,
I wouldn't draw attention to myself, pal .
如果我个头和你一样，我也不会引人注目，朋友。

20
00:04:50,009 --> 00:04:51,079
Give me a break.
让我休息下。

21
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:53,568
We've been wandering with our babies.
我们一直带着孩子们走了半天。

22
00:04:55,037 --> 00:04:57,797
Go ahead. Follow the crowd.
快去吧。跟着大伙。

23
00:04:57,914 --> 00:04:59,519
Be quiet when you're gone.
走的时候，声音小点。

24
00:05:00,831 --> 00:05:02,174
Come on.
走吧。

25
00:05:12,457 --> 00:05:14,487
I'm up, I'm up!
上，上！

26
00:05:17,869 --> 00:05:19,974
Rising sign, everybody.
大家好。

27
00:05:20,478 --> 00:05:22,890
Zeke? Mashu?
齐克？马修？

28
00:05:22,972 --> 00:05:25,993
Birdie? Uncle Fungis?
波尔弟？芬基斯叔叔？

29
00:05:26,194 --> 00:05:27,614
Where is everybody?
大家在哪？

30
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:29,835
Come on, guys.
We gonna miss the mi . . .
来呀。兄弟们，你们将会错过....

31
00:05:30,261 --> 00:05:32,324
My patient.
我的病人。

32
00:05:34,521 --> 00:05:36,398
They left without me.
他们扔下我就走了。

33
00:05:36,478 --> 00:05:39,272
They do this every year!
每年他们都这样！

34
00:05:40,584 --> 00:05:43,652
Why? Doesn't anyone love me?
为什么？为什么没有喜欢我？

35
00:05:43,808 --> 00:05:48,141
Isn't there anyone who cares
about Sid the Sloth?
为什么没有人关心我这树懒--希德。

36
00:05:50,484 --> 00:05:52,458
All right, I'll just go by myself.
没关系，我自己走。

37
00:05:53,587 --> 00:05:56,257
Oh. Stinks!
噢，臭死了！

38
00:05:56,613 --> 00:05:59,325
Hey, wait, buddy!
Tell me next time!
嗨，等一等，兄弟！
下次你得告诉我。

39
00:06:01,734 --> 00:06:04,869
I can't believe it.
Fresh and green.
真不能相信。
它还是绿色新鲜的。

40
00:06:04,995 --> 00:06:07,663
Frank, you're cutest ever.
弗兰克，你真可爱。

41
00:06:07,747 --> 00:06:08,985
Go ahead, pick it.
来呀，捡起它。

42
00:06:09,417 --> 00:06:12,284
A dandelion.
I thought the frost wipe them all out.
蒲公英。
我还以为霜冻把他们都消灭了呢。

43
00:06:12,404 --> 00:06:13,993
All but one.
就剩这一朵了。

44
00:06:16,013 --> 00:06:17,711
Make me so. . .
让我真....

45
00:06:19,504 --> 00:06:23,530
This is definitely not been my day.
You know what I'm saying, buddy?
今天可真倒霉。
你知道我在说什么吧。

46
00:06:23,848 --> 00:06:25,127
What a mess.
真混乱。

47
00:06:25,245 --> 00:06:27,805
Hey, you rhino, you have really
nice race, do you know that?
嗨，犀牛，你跑起来真好看，
你自己知道不？

48
00:06:27,923 --> 00:06:28,848
It's just a fact.
我说的是事实。

49
00:06:30,017 --> 00:06:31,949
You know what I'm talking about.
你知道我在说什么吧。

50
00:06:34,674 --> 00:06:36,217
A dandelion.
蒲公英。

51
00:06:36,341 --> 00:06:38,239
Must be the last one of season.
肯定是这季里的最后一朵。

52
00:06:40,764 --> 00:06:43,080
Carlo.
Easy, Frankie.
卡罗，放松，弗兰克。

53
00:06:43,208 --> 00:06:44,797
He ruined our salad.
他毁了我们的“沙拉”。

54
00:06:44,915 --> 00:06:49,095
Oh, my mistake.
It's my mistake. Let me. . .
噢，是我的错。是我的错。
让我....

55
00:06:49,221 --> 00:06:51,275
No, seriously, let me take care of this.
不，我是认真的，让我们小心这玩意儿。

56
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:53,178
Oh. What is this?
噢，这是什么？

57
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,933
My goodness, that's my favourite.
上帝呀，我最喜欢吃的。

58
00:06:57,795 --> 00:06:59,230
Hmm , delicious.
美味。

59
00:06:59,969 --> 00:07:03,255
That's a. . .good eating.
这可好吃的东西。

60
00:07:03,383 --> 00:07:06,483
Don't let me have it all .
Yes, you have some.
我不能独吞。
你们也尝尝。

61
00:07:06,603 --> 00:07:07,717
Tasty, isn't it?
不错吧？

62
00:07:07,961 --> 00:07:09,271
Gonna have to pick tooth.
我去剔牙了。

63
00:07:10,481 --> 00:07:12,025
Now?
现在？

64
00:07:13,121 --> 00:07:13,772
Now.
现在？

65
00:07:23,828 --> 00:07:24,832
Please save me.
请救救我。

66
00:07:25,962 --> 00:07:27,473
I wanna hit him full speed.
我真想打死他。

67
00:07:27,591 --> 00:07:30,074
That's okay, Frank.
We'll have some fun with him .
好的，弗兰克。
让我们和他玩玩。

68
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:32,672
Don't let them kill me, please.
I wanna live!
请不要让他们杀我。
我想活。

69
00:07:32,788 --> 00:07:33,562
Get off me!
滚开。

70
00:07:33,993 --> 00:07:35,999
Come on, you're making a scene.
来呀，你要出洋相了。

71
00:07:36,126 --> 00:07:38,952
We just take off free and go.
Do your mind?
我们要把他带走，你不介意吧。

72
00:07:39,037 --> 00:07:41,862
Buddy, if not them today,
it's just someone else tomorrow.
兄弟，如果今天不是他们，明日也自有那人。

73
00:07:41,947 --> 00:07:44,462
I rather not be today. Okay?
我宁愿今天没有，好吗？

74
00:07:44,895 --> 00:07:47,720
Gotta break your neck so you
don't feel the pain. How's that?
扭断你的脖子，你就不知道痛了，
怎么样？

75
00:07:47,843 --> 00:07:50,712
Wait a minute.
I thought rhinos are vegetarians.
等一下。在我印象里，犀牛是素食者。

76
00:07:50,831 --> 00:07:52,683
An active point.
Shut up!
说的好！
闭嘴。

77
00:07:52,769 --> 00:07:55,408
Who says we gonna eat him
after we kill him?
谁说杀了他之后，我们要吃他。

78
00:07:55,681 --> 00:07:56,331
Come on, move it.
来吧，开始吧。

79
00:07:56,456 --> 00:07:59,279
You know, I don't like
animals to kill for pleasure.
你知道不，我不喜欢动物为了消遣杀人。

80
00:07:59,404 --> 00:08:00,794
Sid, for matters that cares.
希德，就是我们要杀的。

81
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,700
I'm the matter that cares.
我就是他们要杀的。

82
00:08:02,858 --> 00:08:04,556
Okay, look. If either of you make it
好的，听着。如果你们中有谁

83
00:08:04,681 --> 00:08:07,781
across that sink hole in front of you,
you get this one.
能穿过这个圈进来，他就是你们的了。

84
00:08:07,901 --> 00:08:10,957
That's right, you losers.
You take a step and you're dead.
好的，你们这些失败者。
敢往前你们就死定了。

85
00:08:15,738 --> 00:08:19,145
You're bluffing, huh?
Yeah, that was a bluff.
你在骗人？
是的，我就在骗人。

86
00:08:20,083 --> 00:08:20,776
Go!
上！

87
00:08:56,978 --> 00:08:58,491
A dandelion?
蒲公英？

88
00:09:01,479 --> 00:09:02,482
We're steady!
我们赢了！

89
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:04,615
What?
什么？

90
00:09:11,372 --> 00:09:13,072
You have beautiful eyes.
你的眼睛真漂亮。

91
00:09:13,196 --> 00:09:14,973
Get off my face.
从我脸上下来。

92
00:09:16,532 --> 00:09:18,817
You and me, we make a great team .
你和我在一起，肯定不错。

93
00:09:18,938 --> 00:09:20,249
What do you say
we just head South together?
你说我们向南走怎么样？

94
00:09:20,374 --> 00:09:22,733
Yeah, jump on my back
and relax your whole way.
好的，跳到我背上来，让你一路轻松。

95
00:09:23,050 --> 00:09:24,516
Really?
No.
真的？
骗你的。

96
00:09:24,873 --> 00:09:26,494
Wait, aren't you going to South?
等一下。你不是向南走吗。

97
00:09:26,619 --> 00:09:28,826
The changing season,
emigrational things?
现在可是季节交替，大伙搬家的时候。

98
00:09:29,102 --> 00:09:31,661
Is it ringing a bell?
I guess not, pal .
让你想起了什么？
我想没有。

99
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:34,493
Okay, thanks for the help.
I can take it from here.
好的，谢谢你的帮助。
从这，我可以自己走。

100
00:09:35,582 --> 00:09:39,221
Hey, you over grown weasel .
Wait till we get down there.
嗨，你这个胆小鬼。
敢在那儿等我们下来吗。

101
00:09:40,082 --> 00:09:42,596
The whole South thing is way out.
The heat, the crowd.
南方也没什么好的。天又热，人又多。

102
00:09:43,573 --> 00:09:47,987
This great. You and me, two guys
knocking about in the wild.
这样也好，你和我，俩个人一起在野外闲逛。

103
00:09:48,113 --> 00:09:51,873
No, you just want a bodyguard
so you don't become somebody's side dish.
不，你只需要一个保镖，免得你成了别人的盘中餐。

104
00:09:51,991 --> 00:09:54,276
You're very strut mammoth.
你可真是个“自信”的猛玛象。

105
00:09:54,398 --> 00:09:56,881
Can you lead the way, Mr. Big Guy?
你能带路吗，大块头先生？

106
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,079
Manfred.
曼菲德。

107
00:09:59,131 --> 00:10:02,000
How about Mandy the moody
mammoth or nanny the. . .
曼迪（曼菲德的爱称）这只喜怒无常的猛玛象
怎么样....？

108
00:10:06,812 --> 00:10:08,324
Stop following me.
不要跟着我。

109
00:10:10,498 --> 00:10:13,367
Okay, so you got it.
You won't even know I'm here.
好的。你明白了。我不说话，你根本不知道我在这儿。

110
00:10:13,486 --> 00:10:15,262
I'll just zip the lip when I say. . .
我会闭上嘴的，只有当我说....

111
00:10:57,307 --> 00:11:01,336
Look at the cute little baby, Diego.
看看那可爱的婴儿，迭哥。

112
00:11:03,021 --> 00:11:05,950
Isn't it nice if he joining us for breakfast?
把他当早餐肯定不错。

113
00:11:06,077 --> 00:11:08,304
It wouldn't be breakfast without him .
没了他早餐都没味了。

114
00:11:08,427 --> 00:11:14,061
His daddy wiped our hair for pack.
And rag our skin to keep warm .
他爸爸用我们的毛来包裹，
穿我们的皮来保暖。

115
00:11:14,182 --> 00:11:17,109
And ruin our lives. Don't you think?
毁了我们的生活,你觉的呢?

116
00:11:17,235 --> 00:11:20,710
Let show that human what happen
when he messed with Sabers.
让他们看看惹了我们剑齿虎会有什么下场?

117
00:11:20,838 --> 00:11:23,687
Alert the troops.
We attack at dawn.
让部队警戒。
我们天亮时进攻。

118
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:29,441
And Diego, bring me that baby. Alive.
迭哥，你去把那婴儿带来，要活的。

119
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:34,542
If I'm gonna enjoy my revenge,
I want it to be fresh.
如果我要享受复仇的快感，那孩子死了可不行。

120
00:11:55,959 --> 00:11:57,439
I'm wiped out.
我累死了。

121
00:11:57,682 --> 00:11:58,929
That's your shelter?
那就是你的庇护所？

122
00:11:59,131 --> 00:12:02,259
You're a big guy. You got a lot of
woods. I'm a little guy.
你是个大块头。你能拿这么多木头。
我个头小，我可不行。

123
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,583
You only got a stick.
你只拿了一根木头。

124
00:12:03,711 --> 00:12:08,210
Yeah, but with my little stick,
and my highly evolved brain. . .
是的，用这根小小的木头，再加上
我那高度进化的脑袋.....

125
00:12:08,371 --> 00:12:10,283
I'll start the fire.
我就能生起火起。

126
00:12:10,797 --> 00:12:11,922
Fascinating.
真奇妙。

127
00:12:12,833 --> 00:12:17,097
We'll see if breeze try to blow us
tonight. Now won't we?
今天晚上我们就知道有没有微风吹出来了。
是吧？

128
00:12:22,074 --> 00:12:24,257
Hey, I think I saw its flare.
嗨，我想我看到火花了。

129
00:12:28,731 --> 00:12:32,092
Any chance I can squeeze
in there with you?
我能挤进来吗？

130
00:12:32,215 --> 00:12:34,519
Isn't there someone else you can annoy?
你就不会去烦别人？

131
00:12:34,642 --> 00:12:38,472
Friends? Family?
Poison reptiles?
朋友？家人？
毒虫？

132
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:42,661
My family is bad.
They just kind of migrate without me.
我的家人可不好。
他们每次搬家都不带上我。

133
00:12:43,257 --> 00:12:44,970
You should see what they did last year.
你得看看他们去年做了什么。

134
00:12:45,489 --> 00:12:49,397
They woke up early and
they tied my hands and feet together.
他们早就醒了，然后把我的手脚绑起来。

135
00:12:49,521 --> 00:12:52,682
They buried the cave door,
and covered their tracks.
他们把洞门埋了，又擦了他们足迹。

136
00:12:55,315 --> 00:12:57,821
They made it anyway.
他们就是这样。

137
00:13:02,128 --> 00:13:04,232
So what about you? You got family?
你呢？你有家人吗？

138
00:13:08,471 --> 00:13:11,400
Okay, you're tired, I see.
We'll talk tomorrow morning.
好的，看的出，你累了。
我们明天谈。

139
00:13:13,873 --> 00:13:15,511
Manfred? Manfred.
曼菲德？曼菲德。

140
00:13:15,871 --> 00:13:17,073
Could you move over?
挪过去点儿？

141
00:13:18,533 --> 00:13:20,871
Come on, nobody fall asleep that fast.
不会吧，没人能这么快就睡着了。

142
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:22,794
Mandy!
曼迪？

143
00:16:08,005 --> 00:16:09,915
That's Diego, fall back!
那是迭哥，撤退！

144
00:16:16,295 --> 00:16:17,560
Where's the baby?
那婴儿在哪？

145
00:16:17,636 --> 00:16:20,474
I lost it over the falls.
You lost it?
我在瀑布那儿把他丢了。
你把他丢了。

146
00:16:24,389 --> 00:16:26,605
I want that baby, Diego.
I'll get it.
我要他孩子，迭哥。
我会找回来的。

147
00:16:26,846 --> 00:16:30,567
You better. Unless you want to serve
yourself as the replacement.
最好如此。不然你就要做他的替代品。

148
00:16:30,683 --> 00:16:33,902
We'll go up to half peak. Meet us there.
我们会去半山腰，在那儿见。

149
00:16:34,136 --> 00:16:36,625
It'd better be alive.
最好是活的。

150
00:16:38,128 --> 00:16:40,583
Can we trust you with that, Diego?
我们能相信你吗，迭哥？

151
00:16:40,851 --> 00:16:41,725
Let's go!
我们走！

152
00:17:04,950 --> 00:17:06,706
And you pick this year off my shoulders.
你今年就靠我吧。

153
00:17:06,945 --> 00:17:08,701
If you gonna have a mating partner,
如果你想找个伴侣，

154
00:17:08,825 --> 00:17:11,193
at least pick a female
with the same color palette, right?
起码也得找个同样肤色的，是吧？

155
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:14,341
And I thought, wow, he's gonna go
primal , you know what I'm saying?
我想，他要返朴归真了，你知道我在说什么吧？

156
00:17:14,465 --> 00:17:17,074
If you find a mate in life,
you should be loyal .
如果你找到终生伴侣，你就得对她忠贞。

157
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:19,252
In your case, it's grateful .
Get away from me.
你能这么说，真是让人感动。
离我远点儿。

158
00:17:19,378 --> 00:17:23,973
Well , I think mate in life is stupid.
I mean everybody just sit around. . .
是的，我想“终生伴侣”这个观念简直是可笑。
我是说每人都只是坐在那.....

159
00:17:25,057 --> 00:17:26,551
Mandy?
曼迪？

160
00:18:19,813 --> 00:18:22,913
Look at that.
He's okay.
看看他。
他没事。

161
00:18:33,857 --> 00:18:35,462
She's gone.
她漂走了。

162
00:18:45,368 --> 00:18:47,856
Hey, Mandy,
are you forgetting something?
嗨，曼迪。你没忘什么东西吧？

163
00:18:47,978 --> 00:18:50,314
No.
But you just saved him .
没有。
但是你救了他。

164
00:18:50,434 --> 00:18:53,227
Yeah, but I'm still trying
to get rid of the last thing I saved.
是的，我还想摆脱我上一次救的东西呢。

165
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:55,150
You can't leave him here.
